      "portraitFile": "Kamui.png",
      "sourceSheet": "神威",
      "status": "accepted",
      "names": {
        "en": "Corrin",
        "ja": "カムイ",
        "jaLatn": "Kamui",
        "zhHans": "神威"
      },
      "gender": "variable",
      "dragonVein": true,
      "unitTags": [
        "dragon"
      ],
      "personalSkillId": "supportive",
      "notes": [
        {
          "text": "Corrin's display name, gender, boon, bane, and Talent are selected by the player.",
          "textZhHans": "神威的显示名称、性别、增益、减益与天赋均由玩家选择。"
        },
        {
          "text": "Corrin begins with the Bronze Sword in the Prologue, then receives Ganglari in Chapter 2, the Dragonstone in Chapter 5, and Yato in Chapter 6.",
          "textZhHans": "神威在序章持有青铜剑，随后在第2章获得刚加拉尔，第5章获得龙石，第6章获得夜刀神。"
        },
        {
          "text": "Corrin's Dragonstone weapon rank is absent during the early game and appears at D after Dragonstone access unlocks in Chapter 5.",
          "textZhHans": "神威的龙石武器等级在前期不存在，待第5章解锁龙石后以 D 级出现。"
        }
      ],
      "supportNotes": [
        "Corrin can support every normally playable character. Same-gender A supports unlock Friendship Seal access without choosing a single A+ partner; opposite-gender S supports unlock Partner Seal access, with Niles and Rhajat as same-gender S-support exceptions.",
        "To keep every child paralogue obtainable, male Corrin must marry a female Corrin-exclusive partner (a Corrinsexual) or a female offspring unit other than Kana. Marrying a standard first-generation bachelorette leaves another father's child paralogue permanently unavailable; marrying Niles also prevents Kana and Nina's paralogues."
      ],
      "supportNotesZhHans": [
        "神威可与所有可正常使用的角色支援。同性别 A 级支援无需固定一名 A+ 搭档即可解锁友情之证获取；异性别 S 级支援可解锁婚姻之证获取，其中零与莎拉是同性别 S 支援的例外。",
        "为使所有子女外传都可获得，男神威必须与仅限神威的女性搭档（Corrinsexual）或除神流以外的女性子女单位结婚。若与普通的初代女性单身角色结婚，会使另一位父亲的子女外传永久无法获得；与零结婚还会阻止神流与艾潘妮的外传。"
      ]
    },
